<p>Set the editor background to a random picture from a folder.</p>
<p>The plug-in is based on <a href="https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/8502-background-image-plus">Background Image Plus</a></p>

<h2>中文说明：</h2>
<p>给编辑器添加图片背景，将编辑器背景设置为文件夹中的随机图片。</p>
<p>该插件是在<a href="https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/8502-background-image-plus">Background Image Plus</a>的基础上开发完成</p>

